1. View Tasks
    1.1. Need "View Tasks" button on GUI
    1.2. Clicking View Tasks should open a new window with all task information.
    1.3. View Tasks UI should give the ability to complete tasks
    1.4. View Tasks UI should have the ability to sort data
    1.5. Task Details in View Tasks UI should be truncated.
    1.6. Double Clicking on a task in View Tasks UI should provide an ability to pop out the task with all of the details.